is the boat turning over.

26:38.265 --> 26:39.733
How do you end up here?

26:43.370 --> 26:44.705
I don't know.

26:46.273 --> 26:47.641
Miss Naomi

26:48.342 --> 26:49.743
kind of adopted me.

27:05.693 --> 27:06.794
I'm also an orphan.

27:10.698 --> 27:12.766
I always dreamed
a family would adopt me.

27:14.368 --> 27:15.669
No one ever did.

27:19.707 --> 27:20.941
Where do you live now?

27:22.309 --> 27:24.245
