my entire life.

27:25.346 --> 27:27.148
They're like my sisters.

27:27.181 --> 27:29.416
Do you remember anything
about your real family?

27:31.152 --> 27:32.186
My grandma.

27:34.822 --> 27:35.956
It's less every day.

27:40.361 --> 27:42.296
